OL,5,G1315 Songs of Praise: Faith across the
OL,6,G     Generations
OL,7,     FClaire McCollum explores the joys
OL,8,     Fof connecting generations and how
OL,9,     Ffaith plays a part.
OL,10,G1350 Points of View
OL,11,     F9/20. Viewers have their say on
OL,12,     Fthe BBC's television programmes.
OL,13,     FEmail your thoughts to
OL,14,     Fpov@bbc.co.uk, tweet @bbcPoV or
OL,15,     Fsearch Facebook for BBC Points of
OL,16,     FView.
OL,17,G1405 Lifeline
OL,18,     FJeff Brazier presents an appeal on
OL,19,     Fbehalf of the Katie Piper
OL,20,     FFoundation, a charity that helps
OL,21,     Fsurvivors of burns and trauma
OL,22,     Frecover and rebuild their lives.
