OL,5,G1415 The Americas
OL,6,     F9/11. This episode focuses on the
OL,7,     Fbehaviour of animals living on and
OL,8,     Fclose to the West Coast, including
OL,9,     Fsea wolves, giant Pacific
OL,10,     Foctopuses, sea otters, salamanders
OL,11,     Fand blue whales.
OL,12,G1500 The Americas
OL,13,     F10/11. This episode features the
OL,14,     Fbehaviour of animals living in and
OL,15,     Fnear Patagonia, including
OL,16,     Frockhopper penguins, pumas,
OL,17,     FChilean stag beetles, Darwin's
OL,18,     Frheas, orcas and elephant seals.
